      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just a \"moment\" though. it’s the reality of who i am now. i've spent years building a version of myself that doesn't exist anymore. honestly, trying to \"move forward\" just feels like a chore i don't have the strength for. everything feels so quiet and heavy. i just want the noise to stop. it feels like accepting that it's over is the only way to actually find some peace.",
